Pat,

You are gonna be mad if you brake them off inside the tubes.  :-(

Go easy, push and pull on both ends...apply a lubricant liberally
down the tubes.  Triple check for crushed metal tubing.

If it is crushed you will be curring that part off anyway.

Cheers, dave

